mdRecord.dcterms:title: Dulaney Family Cemetery, Indian Valley District
mdRecord.dcterms:description: Located adjacent to 835 White Rock Rd NW. There is a small drive way up to the cemetery which is on the right. Cemetery is enclosed in a fence and well maintained. It is difficult to see from the road and not visible on Google Earth due to tree cover. N 36 57.161' W 080 28.789'
